DynamicTimeWarps.diff_description:
Dynamic Time Warp applied for two time series from given column within a given stage.
The figure gives a visual comparison representation between series.

TimeTwoEvents.diff_description:
A time difference between two events is calculated for each Ollie performance (commit and reference). 
Then those time differences are compared to determine how close both intervals are, 
and in which direction the next commit should be taken.
